summary: A small open world house on the edge of the Rift with an archery range. Recommended for Archers
descriptionHtml:
Hello!
This is the mod for a small home on the edge of the Rift where the \'Autumn\' forest ends and pine trees begin.

-The house is marked and there are no enchanted weapons or over-powered armor.

-It\'s simple it\'s small, perfect for a ranger in the forest type character.

-The range is located just to the North of the main house with three targets

There will be bug fixes, If there are any bugs. It should be just fine. As the mod should be 100% functional

Please endorse and suggest houses and or other mods for me! :D

Enjoy!
author: Chanson93
